  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "In a Korean brass bowl, mix together sliced Kenyan chorizo, fresh papillote, chopped kale, and cooked quinoa",
    "Drizzle lemon juice and olive oil over the top of the mixture",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste",
    "Cover the bowl with a lid and let it sit for 10 minutes to allow the flavors to meld",
    "Serve the Intense Kenyan Chorizo Bowl hot, garnished with additional papillote if desired"
